Package: libopencog-attention
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
         libatomspace (>= 5.0.5),
         libcogutil (>= 1.0.0)
Description: OpenCog attention mechanisms library (runtime)
 The Attention module provides attention allocation and control
 mechanisms for the OpenCog cognitive architecture, enabling
 selective focus and resource management.
 .
 This package contains the shared libraries for runtime use.

Package: libopencog-attention-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libopencog-attention (= ${binary:Version}),
         libatomspace-dev (>= 5.0.5),
         libcogutil-dev (>= 1.0.0),
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: OpenCog attention mechanisms library (development files)
 The Attention module provides attention allocation and control
 mechanisms for the OpenCog cognitive architecture, enabling
 selective focus and resource management.
 .
 This package contains the header files and development libraries.
